Text: thankyou ms fenmore,we love you here in oz.

Thank you...welcome back...hope you had a great Labour Day weekend.  They don't celebrate that here in Central America.  Mind you they have more holidays here than any country I know of.  lol lol lol  In the month of November there are 17 days that are holidays!  They love to party, drink cerveza, rum and shoot off their fireworks.
